					"dataType": "talent",
					"elementDisplay": "<p chunk_id=\"a4c78ed7-13c0-4670-98c9-ca7a9005bff2\" class=\"CORE-paragraph-styles_CORE-stat\"><strong><span class=\"color-span\">Prerequisite:</span></strong>\n<tooltip category=\"talent\" class=\"tooltip-convert\" element=\"true-stoneshaping\" nexus=\"cosmererpg\">True Stoneshaping</tooltip> talent\n</p>\n<p chunk_id=\"91529b92-19e8-4f26-862d-d395f2ed6f35\" class=\"CORE-paragraph-styles_CORE-stat\"><strong><span class=\"color-span\">Act</span></strong><strong><span class=\"color-span\">ivation:</span></strong> <span aria-label=\"Special Activation\" class=\"icon-font icon\" title=\"Special Activation\">★</span></p>\n<div chunk_id=\"08adcc82-9c6d-4e4b-870b-83fdf8080233\" class=\"lore-block\" style=\"\">\n<p class=\"\"><em>Shaping stone with Cohesion has become so natural that you can mold the ground beneath your feet as you actively sculpt other stone.</em></p>\n</div>\n<p chunk_id=\"60242f59-b3dd-4755-b4a5-c6d729a29766\" class=\"CORE-paragraph-styles_CORE-body\">After you use Cohesion or spend at least <span aria-label=\"One Action\" class=\"icon-font icon\" title=\"One Action\">▶</span> on one of its talents, you can shape the stone beneath your feet without spending additional <tooltip category=\"rule\" class=\"tooltip-convert\" element=\"investiture\" nexus=\"cosmererpg\">Investiture</tooltip> to do so. The stone pushes you up to 5 feet × your ranks in Cohesion, and you can choose to be pushed in any direction, such as rising upward on a pillar. This movement doesn’t trigger <tooltip category=\"action\" class=\"tooltip-convert\" element=\"reactive-strike\" nexus=\"cosmererpg\">Reactive Strikes</tooltip>.</p>",
