					"elementDisplay": "<p chunk_id=\"4e08b199-4797-4650-bd34-aedf147f69eb\" class=\"CORE-paragraph-styles_CORE-stat\"><strong><span class=\"color-span\">Prerequisite:</span></strong>\n<tooltip category=\"talent\" class=\"tooltip-convert\" element=\"sinkhole\" nexus=\"cosmererpg\">Sinkhole</tooltip> talent\n</p>\n<p chunk_id=\"86c80a27-a5e2-4826-ac73-0e9125135b3f\" class=\"CORE-paragraph-styles_CORE-stat\"><strong><span class=\"color-span\">Activation:</span></strong> <span aria-label=\"Always Active\" class=\"icon-font icon\" title=\"Always Active\">∞</span></p>\n<div chunk_id=\"2ca47503-163d-4981-ac7a-cdcd241bb2a2\" class=\"lore-block\" style=\"\">\n<p class=\"\"><em>When you touch stone, you can sense and use your Cohesion through it from a much greater distance.</em></p>\n</div>\n<p chunk_id=\"af9e3f35-083b-4ce5-8a22-e8cac5850f11\" class=\"CORE-paragraph-styles_CORE-body\">You can use your surges and their talents as though your <tooltip category=\"rule\" class=\"tooltip-convert\" element=\"reach\" nexus=\"cosmererpg\">reach</tooltip> is 20 feet, as long as there is a stone surface between you and your target that you can touch.</p>",
