					"_highlightResult": {
						"elementDisplay": {
							"value": "<p chunk_id=\"4e08b199-4797-4650-bd34-aedf147f69eb\" class=\"CORE-paragraph-styles_CORE-stat\"><strong><span class=\"color-span\">Prerequisite:</span></strong>\n<tooltip category=\"talent\" class=\"tooltip-convert\" element=\"sinkhole\" nexus=\"cosmererpg\">Sinkhole</tooltip> talent\n</p>\n<p chunk_id=\"86c80a27-a5e2-4826-ac73-0e9125135b3f\" class=\"CORE-paragraph-styles_CORE-stat\"><strong><span class=\"color-span\">Activation:</span></strong> <span aria-label=\"Always Active\" class=\"icon-font icon\" title=\"Always Active\">∞</span></p>\n<div chunk_id=\"2ca47503-163d-4981-ac7a-cdcd241bb2a2\" class=\"lore-block\" style=\"\">\n<p class=\"\"><em>When you touch stone, you can sense and use your Cohesion through it from a much greater distance.</em></p>\n</div>\n<p chunk_id=\"af9e3f35-083b-4ce5-8a22-e8cac5850f11\" class=\"CORE-paragraph-styles_CORE-body\">You can use your surges and their talents as though your <tooltip category=\"rule\" class=\"tooltip-convert\" element=\"reach\" nexus=\"cosmererpg\">reach</tooltip> is 20 feet, as long as there is a stone surface between you and your target that you can touch.</p>",
							"matchLevel": "none",
							"matchedWords": []
						},
						"name": {
							"value": "Through the Stone",
							"matchLevel": "none",
							"matchedWords": []
						},
						"shortDescription": {
							"value": "You can use your surges and their talents as though your reach is 20 feet.",
							"matchLevel": "none",
							"matchedWords": []
						}
					}
				},
				{
					"dataType": "talent",
					"elementDisplay": "<p chunk_id=\"a8736c4d-8b07-4c2c-a0c7-5528fdb43ee3\" class=\"CORE-paragraph-styles_CORE-stat\"><strong><span class=\"color-span\">Prerequisite:</span></strong> Cohesion 2+; <tooltip category=\"talent\" class=\"tooltip-convert\" element=\"tunneling\" nexus=\"cosmererpg\">Tunneling</tooltip> talent</p>\n<p chunk_id=\"0840c171-30a7-4711-9f59-2d72021a05be\" class=\"CORE-paragraph-styles_CORE-stat\"><strong><span class=\"color-span\">Act</span></strong><strong><span class=\"color-span\">ivation:</span></strong> <span aria-label=\"Always Active\" class=\"icon-font icon\" title=\"Always Active\">∞</span></p>\n<div chunk_id=\"3fe20524-6fb0-49ae-86c6-a5f786fa834a\" class=\"lore-block\" style=\"\">\n<p class=\"\"><em>You no longer simply soften stone—you assert your will on it, molding it into complex shapes with a mere command.</em></p>\n</div>\n<p chunk_id=\"bca57b5a-cc89-4d03-9fdd-3ed5ee0bdcb8\" class=\"CORE-paragraph-styles_CORE-body\">When you use Cohesion to shape an object or surface, you can automatically reshape it to your will without using additional actions or time. For example, you can instantly raise or lower elevation, form walls or pillars, create or remove <tooltip category=\"rule\" class=\"tooltip-convert\" element=\"difficult-terrain\" nexus=\"cosmererpg\">difficult terrain</tooltip>, or create intricate shapes or images.</p>",
