				{
					"dataType": "talent",
					"elementDisplay": "<p chunk_id=\"83c478c0-e3e5-4f8d-a2f0-5ecd746d06a5\" class=\"CORE-paragraph-styles_CORE-stat\"><strong><span class=\"color-span\">Prerequisite:</span></strong>\n<tooltip category=\"talent\" class=\"tooltip-convert\" element=\"sinkhole\" nexus=\"cosmererpg\">Sinkhole</tooltip> talent\n</p>\n<p chunk_id=\"db78276b-9576-40f6-b470-33327c1a045f\" class=\"CORE-paragraph-styles_CORE-stat\"><strong><span class=\"color-span\">Act</span></strong><strong><span class=\"color-span\">ivation:</span></strong> <span aria-label=\"One Action\" class=\"icon-font icon\" title=\"One Action\">▶</span></p>\n<div chunk_id=\"5e2c22d3-bc49-460f-a66e-b379ce662fe3\" class=\"lore-block\" style=\"\">\n<p class=\"\"><em>You infuse yourself with Cohesion to shift stone from your path as you move.</em></p>\n</div>\n<p chunk_id=\"1496ddd8-2cba-4ef0-86d6-f82f5a6e5509\" class=\"CORE-paragraph-styles_CORE-body\">Spend 1 Investiture to infuse yourself with Cohesion. For the duration, you can move through stone surfaces and objects as if moving through <tooltip category=\"rule\" class=\"tooltip-convert\" element=\"difficult-terrain\" nexus=\"cosmererpg\">difficult terrain</tooltip>. You leave a 5-foot-radius tunnel in your wake through which others can follow. At the start of each of your turns, you can spend 1 Investiture as <span aria-label=\"Free Action\" class=\"icon-font icon\" title=\"Free Action\">▷</span> to maintain this infusion.</p>\n<p chunk_id=\"0ac951b5-4d6d-4748-8b6b-f16dc3eb42c9\" class=\"CORE-paragraph-styles_CORE-body\">If you create tunnels near the surface, an observant character might detect ripples from the diverted material, potentially sensing your presence.</p>",
